Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think that the answer to this tends to depend on the person. Some people thrive in social settings. Some people don't care. And others do not do well at all. Personal psychology is rarely taken into account. I think it would be a good thing if it were.